Senator Dino Melaye, representing Kogi West senatorial district has revealed that the state government was planning to frame him up for murder, using security and judiciary apparatus. It would be recalled that the senator has been having a running battle with the state governor Yahaya Bello. In a series of tweets on Monday, Senator Melaye said he has evidence that the state government intends to use the Inspector General of Police as well as the Attorney General of the Federation to frame up a murder case against him. “Kogi State govt trying to frame me up again for murder in the second assassination attempt on my life on June 12 2017 in Lokoja. “Fools always forget the God factor in the affairs of men. Their design is to bombard me with cases using the Police and AGF. I refuse to be intimidated,” he tweeted.  Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook